MultiFileRAG System
The MultiFileRAG System is a specialized implementation of LightRAG for processing PDF, CSV, and image files, providing enhanced data analysis, visualization, and querying capabilities powered by local LLMs through Ollama.

Local LLM Integration
Local LLM Integration uses Ollama to run models locally without relying on external APIs, a key feature of the MultiFileRAG System.

PDF Processing
The MultiFileRAG System extracts text and insights from PDF files, one of its primary features.<SEP>The system extracts text and insights from PDF files, one of its primary features.

CSV Processing
The system also processes CSV files to extract text, statistics, and insights.<SEP>The system processes CSV files to extract text, statistics, and insights, providing valuable insights into the data.

Image Processing
Metadata and descriptions can be extracted from image files using the MultiFileRAG System, enhancing its capabilities.<SEP>Metadata and descriptions can be extracted from image files using the MultiFileRAG System.

Advanced Querying
The system supports advanced querying across multiple file types using LightRAG's various modes, providing users with more control over their queries.<SEP>The system supports advanced querying across multiple file types using LightRAG's various modes.

Web UI
A user-friendly interface allows users to upload files and query the system effectively, making it accessible for all users.<SEP>A user-friendly interface allows users to upload files and query the system effectively.

LightRAG
LightRAG is a specialized implementation of LightRAG for processing PDF, CSV, and image files, providing enhanced data analysis, visualization, and querying capabilities powered by local LLMs through Ollama.

Ollama
Ollama is the technology that enables local LLM integration with the MultiFileRAG System, allowing for API-free processing of files.
